data.description: This beautifully designed, solidly built, immaculately maintained home sits on 1.1 rolling acres on a quiet but accessible road in the Town of Newburgh. Three bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, master bathroom includes jetted bathtub, separate shower. Roof was replaced in July 2023.  Other features include vaulted entryway, hardwood floors, eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, full dining room, wood-burning fireplace in living room, heated inground pool and back yard have plenty of sun and plenty of privacy. Finished basement is dry as a bone and features a huge amount of storage space, second full sized fridge/freezer, and definitely has a lot of potential for entertaining or possibly a future fourth bedroom. Other features include whole-house automatic hard-wired backup generator, central air, central vacuum, large walk-in closet in master bedroom, security system, two-car garage, and you're less than 15 min to the metro north train, 5 minutes to I-84, 10 minutes to the thruway.
